snippet.title: Sea Power Announcement Teaser
snippet.description:
Add to your wishlist: https://bit.ly/3qTd4ZI

Find out more at:
https://www.microprose.com/games/sea-power
https://discord.gg/xyWqGak
https://twitter.com/TriassicGames
https://www.facebook.com/Triassic-Games-105804100925194/
From the creative mind behind Cold Waters, Sea Power lets you control NATO and Warsaw Pact forces in modern naval conflict campaigns. Use your advanced naval weaponry and sensors to respect rules of engagement and defeat the enemy forces in a tense fight for initiative and air/naval supremacy.
